TITLE: Direct Event Handler Attachment using Mutation Listener in Lexical
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to attach event handlers directly to specific DOM nodes using a mutation listener. Includes handling for node creation and updates while maintaining a WeakSet to track registered elements.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/lexical/blob/main/packages/lexical-website/docs/concepts/dom-events.md#2025-04-13_snippet_1

